reviewText: some of it did not jell, like them being on the island when they spent the night before D day good battle field coverage
Picture was all scrambled like puzzle and the audio was all totally unclear. I want to return this DVD and have it replaced.
If you like world war II movies this is one for your collection as usual boy meets girl but the action is very good in one of the bloodiest battles of the war.
i received the product on time as promised, that was important to me. i hope to watch the movie very soon.  thank you
